## 🎯 Real-World Use Cases

### Scenario 1: Early Flood Warning

Meteorologists can enter rainfall data and receive instant flood risk predictions, enabling timely evacuation planning.

### Scenario 2: Resource Allocation

Disaster response teams can monitor multiple regions and prioritize relief efforts.

### Scenario 3: Policy and Planning

Government agencies can validate predictions against historical records and improve flood mitigation strategies.

